name: quality-seeds-fork
title: Quality Seeds
author: SoulCRYSIS
description:
This mod gives you a reason to have high quality seeds. 
Adds a custom Greenhouse cultivator for every plant (Wood, Yumako, and Jellystem + will affect other modded plants!) 
Plants that release spores will release twice as many spores, via a new spores fluid. 
Spores can be released back into the atmosphere at a controlled location by destroying their containing entity, or using a Spore Vent.
Finally, there is now also the end-game treat of plants in space!
